@Mynameislegion: Yeah, you need to change the .html files, here is a simple python script that do this for you:
```
import os, re

for root, dirs, files in os.walk("."):
    for file in files:
        if not file.endswith(".html"):
            continue
        data = open(root + "/" + file).read()
        if not '<ul class="languages">' in data:
            continue

        content, footer = data.split('<ul class="languages">')

        new_footer = re.sub('(href="[\\./]+/[a-zA-Z-]+)/', "\\1.tar.gz/", footer)
        open(root + "/" + file, "w").write(content + '<ul class="languages">' + new_footer)
```

